data.description: Welcome to this charming Ranch Style Home nestled in the heart of Aurora, Colorado. Boasting 716 finished square feet, this cozy abode offers a comfortable and efficient living space. With 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, it's the perfect size for a small family or those seeking a manageable living space.  The updated kitchen adds a modern touch to the home, making meal preparation a breeze. A detached 2 car garage provides ample parking and storage options. Situated on a spacious lot, there's plenty of room for outdoor activities, gardening, or expansion possibilities.  Convenience is key, as this property is conveniently located near multiple shopping centers, ensuring that all your retail and dining needs are just a stone's throw away. Additionally, the home falls within the desirable Aurora Public Schools district, making it an excellent choice for families with school-age children.  Built in 1949, this home carries a sense of history while offering modern comfort. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer or looking to downsize without sacrificing style, this Ranch Style Home in Aurora is a must-see, blending classic charm with contemporary convenience.
